<% content_for :page_title, "Start page" %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Determine and evaluate the level of risk presented by a consumer product</h1>
    <p class="govuk-body-l">The assessment will be undertaken using the recently introduced Product Safety Risk Assessment Methodology (PRISM) which is intended for use by organisations responsible for market surveillance and enforcement.</p>
    <p class="govuk-body">You can find the <abbr title="Product Safety Risk Assessment Methodology">PRISM</abbr> guide, examples of <abbr title="Product Safety Risk Assessment Methodology">PRISM</abbr> risk assessments and statistical data sets to support your risk assessments on the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/product-safety-risk-assessment-methodology-prism" class="govuk-link" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><abbr title="Product Safety Risk Assessment Methodology">PRISM</abbr> guidance page<span class="govuk-visually-hidden"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>. An explanation of <abbr title="Office for Product Safety and Standards">OPSS</abbr> terminology concerned with risk and risk-related matters can be found on the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/opss-risk-lexicon" class="govuk-link" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><abbr title="Office for Product Safety and Standards">OPSS</abbr> risk lexicon page<span class="govuk-visually-hidden"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.</p>
    <p class="govuk-body">Use this service to:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Undertake <a href="<%= perform_risk_triage_path %>" class="govuk-link">risk triage</a> to determine whether the product needs a full safety risk assessment.</li>
      <li>Search for products on the Product Safety Database (PSD).</li>
      <li>Assess and evaluate the risk presented by general consumer products.</li>
      <li>Save and submit assessment results to the <abbr title="Product Safety Database">PSD</abbr>.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">You will need:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Product Safety Database (PSD) login credentials - weâ€™ll ask you to sign in or <a href="mailto:opss.enquiries@businessandtrade.gov.uk" class="govuk-link">request a new account</a> before starting the full risk assessment.</li>
      <li>Information about the product, including details of the manufacturer/supplier, number of products sold, and other information accompanying the product.</li>
      <li>Details of safety concerns associated with the product including number and nature of hazards.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="govuk-body">Also, the following information is likely to be useful and relevant in many circumstances:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Product test reports.</li>
      <li>Any relevant research studies, statistical data sets or other evidence to indicate the probability of harm occurring and the nature of the harm.</li>
      <li>Any risk assessments that have been undertaken previously for the type of product being assessed, or for closely related products.</li>
    </ul>
    <%= govuk_start_button(text: "Start now", href: serious_risk_path) %>
  </div>
</div>
